channel.title: Project Catalyst
channel.description:
Hello, my name is Andrew and I come to you with a BRAND NEW 718 economy server. This is my first release, and I hope you guys like it, I have never worked on anything above 317, the only source/client I've messed with was the RuneLocus starter pack. Hope you guys like it :)
===================================== Features ===================================== 1- Full NEX 2- Full GWD 3- Corporeal Best 4- Full Squeal of Fortune 5- Full Dominion Tower 6- Full QBD all four phases 7- 90% Dicing, (only works in old item looks) 8- Tormented Demons 9- Rock Crabs 10- Yaks 11- LRC (Living Rock Caverns) 12- Fight Caves (Automatically skips to wave 63) 13 - 100% 5 phase Fight Kiln 14- Good staff, (need some) 15- Shops ==================================== Not that much, but meh, I think I did pretty good for a solo creation.
PICTURES/MEDIA [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3269014/Bandos_GWD.PNG[/img] [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3269027/Corp.PNG[/img] CORP HAS BEEN ADDED AS OF APRIL 28TH 2013 [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3269030/Dicing___Home.PNG[/img] [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3269037/DomTower.PNG[/img] [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3269043/Full_Nex.PNG[/img] [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3269049/Tormented_Demons.PNG[/img] [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3269052/QBD.PNG[/img] [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3269057/SOF.PNG[/img] [img]http://www.upload.ee/thumb/3269058/SOF2.PNG[/img] [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/3269060/Rock_Crabs.PNG[/img]
